title: 47.Ronin.3D.2013.1080p.DTS5.1.MP4Plex
description:
Full screen with no black bars at top and bottom, for the full 3D effect. Excellent DTS 5.1 audio, and higher bitrate for better video. Always use better than the Plex Media Server minimum system requirements when transcoding larger 3D files - even if they are the more DLNA friendly MP4 format. And if you can connect directly to a router that your 3D TV is plugged into via ethernet instead of wireless, you'll increase the probability of a smoother transcode!

And PLEASE SEED at least 3 times the original file size so others can benefit just as much as you!!
